{"tid":1473581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求文宣組入】【國際文宣】比個機會外國人出一份力","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:51:28.000Z","uid":229835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d19cc78db60f355118fb3a4d57f995245877b91","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:35:09.000Z","msg":"小弟有個諗法<br />\n<br />\n大家係機埸既時候應該發現<br />\n其實可能好多外國人都知發生緊咩事<br />\n<strong>但係點關心都好都唔會好似香港人咁肉緊，畢竟唔係自己屋企</strong><br />\n當佢地離開左香港<br />\n好快個種關心就會好快變成食花生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以不如我地比埋個機會佢地為香港付出<br />\n真正令佢地既關心變成行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n1.印定一大堆信，封信既內容就可能係話，&quot;本人非常關注香港所發生既不公義之事，希望得知官方既睇法之類&quot;<br />\n之後根據個個外國人既國籍，成封信連埋信封比佢，<br />\n而佢要做既只係當番到自己既國家時，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寄向佢地自己國家既政府機構</span></strong><br />\n佢地付出既只係郵票錢，但係就將佢地既關心用實際行動表達左<br />\n<br />\n2.可能做一個類似FB CHALLENGE 之類既野，支持香港既話，<br />\n就拎住塊牌影一影相放上FACEBOOK之後TAG 3個人個樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">總之個重點要係付出唔駛多(我諗關心得既話唔會介意影張相或者個少少郵票錢)<br />\n但係又可以令佢地表明立埸支持我地</span></strong><br />\n信既內容同寄去邊都可以再諗<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗??<br />\n大家比D意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯請屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4969387ec8d80d3acc8b4b6cea070d4a898a86","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"eb516b37e7e307677c19849a3f854d92cfa08192","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:36:17.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"f5890ce5f76ede86522cf9050888ae7d7ec94b39","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ac1d9f871ba53b1cc187774a780613f8f6e94874","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8b7f32bef6332b373f71278f97008a40d2c6859c","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"8b01a65d6db78f7dac212a4aadea6babb140684e","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:37:29.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4015ef0fb195e3d4f464c8a631f0b63d0dae4157","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:37:45.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"836e0a11287253280a55efa9e195a055a1a7e613","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:37:56.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"34231e80413963ce75eaf2d4abf7bfe274102152","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:38:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c6eac761bcc75309f902f5e192560d32b4cb1b87","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:38:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bf144b784c4640556e358e8e5b88fe3bcbb867fb","tid":1473581,"uid":229835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"299cf1ebb88f07d32251c0a773f91e385c9e8a8d","tid":1473581,"uid":31110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n818 叫埋外國人"}]}